steps.html_instructions: Head east on E San Francisco St toward Cathedral Pl
Take the 1st left onto Old Santa Fe Trail
Turn right onto the Interstate 25 S ramp to Albuquerque
Take exit 226A-226B for I-40 E/I-40 W toward Santa Rosa/Gallup

Keep right at the fork to continue on Exit 226B, follow signs for Gallup/I-40 W and merge onto I-40 W
Passing through Arizona
Entering California
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-15 S, follow signs for Los Angeles/San Diego
Take the exit onto CA-210 W toward Pasadena
Take the I-10 exit toward Los Angeles/San Bernardino
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for I-10 W/San Bernardino Fwy/Los Angles and merge onto I-10 W/San Bernardino Fwy
Keep left at the fork to continue on San Bernardino Fwy, follow signs for U.S. 101/Los Angeles

Turn left onto W 1st St
Destination will be on the right
